The Top 20 Global Concert Tours ranks artists by average box office gross per city and includes the average ticket price for shows Worldwide. The list is based on data provided to the trade publication Pollstar by concert promoters and venue managers. Week of 3/13/2023 : TOP 20 GLOBAL CONCERT TOURS 1. Red Hot Chili Peppers 2. Elton John 3. Bad Bunny 4. Harry Styles 5. Daddy Yankee 6. Carin León 7. Marc Anthony 8. The Killers 9. The Cure 10. Trans-Siberian Orchestra 11. André Rieu 12. Wisin & Yandel 13. Stromae 14. Pentatonix 15. Rosalía 16. The 1975 17. Jo Koy 18. Luke Bryan 19. Bryan Adams 20. Nightwish For free upcoming tour information, go to www.pollstar.com ___